WEBVTT

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:00.816
at 20 million dollars apiece,

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:04.296
and give over 80,000 artists

00:03:04.320 --> 00:03:07.400
an annual salary of 50,000 dollars each.

00:03:08.200 --> 00:03:11.456
If that's only 0.05 percent,

00:03:11.480 --> 00:03:13.440
imagine what a full one percent could do.

00:03:14.920 --> 00:03:17.616
Now, I know we live
in a capitalist society,

00:03:17.640 --> 00:03:19.720
and profits matter a lot.

00:03:20.760 --> 00:03:23.600
So let's look at it
from a financial angle, shall we?

00:03:24.280 --> 00:03:26.656
The US nonprofit arts industry

00:03:26.680 --> 00:03:32.496
generates more than 166 billion dollars
in economic activity,